SubjectRepublic of Turkey - Double Taxation Agreement Ratification
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the necessary action to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF TURKEY for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital.
